<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Interchangeably" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Interchangeably,</orth> 1) in return: <cit><quote>and i. hurl down my gage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.146" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 146</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) mutually: <cit><quote>and i. set down their hands,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 98</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>being sealed i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.81" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 81</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in witness whereof the parties i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 62</bibl></cit>.
